               <msContents>
                  <summary>A rather fragmentary contract in which a share in a house located in the city of Antinoopolis is sold. The parties involved in the contract are mainly unknown, although it is clear that two of these persons were Roman citizens, enrolled by phyles and demes in the city.</summary>
